title: Feature/#5 remember my password
body:
feature: Add email-based password reset functionality and add password reset option to user profile:

Implemented a "Remember Me" feature allowing users to reset their password via email. The system generates a secure token sent to the user's registered email, guiding them to set a new password and integrated a password reset option directly in the user profile, enabling users to securely create a new password.
